Audit-Sector Proposals Will Be ‘Ambitious,’ EU Commission Says

-- B y   A o i f e   W h i t e
-- 
2011-09-27T10:37:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-27/audit-sector-proposals-will-be-ambitious-eu-commission-says.html
The European Commission said it
will make “ambitious” proposals to regulate the audit
industry, with plans scheduled to be published as soon as
November.  “The audit sector displayed clear failings during the
crisis and this is why we believe more has to be done,” said
 Chantal Hughes , a spokeswoman for the commission in Brussels
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
